{"tid":1347031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我突然覺得好有希望","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:02:07.000Z","uid":113716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4436d7b97d18c162901fce3fefcfa47b7b5f246f","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"1. 香港人終於睇清警黑合作呢事實 <br />\n其實一早已經係咁 但今次運動多咗咁多人參與 加上琴日佢地on99打埋路人 認清呢個事實嘅人多咗好多<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港人連鄉黑都唔撚驚<br />\n琴晚發夢啲人吹雞光復元朗又好 呢兩日入元朗都好 我地唔撚驚呀屌你 <br />\n<br />\n3. 全民皆兵<br />\n今日元朗 聽日可能係你嗰區 睇到全港勇武起嚟 只為自衛 同守護家園 唔洗再受和理非束縛<br />\n<br />\n4. 政府角色弱化 迎接我地第一次嘅普選啦!!<br />\n<br />\n多謝鄉黑嘅鄉親父老 我地又向前邁進一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bd39b22744a69b26545c12301c9ee3e3cbb982","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"35c564619df34026727acf5e1ba44975e1265479","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"55459a04748de6a7f7e42e55f3597d4db669d77e","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cd36bb124b3ecfd7ff0f68602bbbbf74663840a7","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8114e4ed79b6338ee68caf2d89d37e2c889b0aab","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8e10ec2ffeea165bc18ba00738735960876f3bc2","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b4537898e9171311f04326f6372dac3881741bcb","tid":1347031,"uid":113716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bcc45e1707d352a3c89aa948